# Cooked room / texture / model blobs land here via
# `make cook-playtest` or the editor's embedded Play action.
# They're a deterministic function of the editor's project state
# and easy to regenerate, so committing them would churn diffs
# every time someone cooks. The tracked `level_manifest.rs`
# stays as a buildable placeholder with no references to these
# ignored files.
rooms/*.psxw
textures/*.psxt
models/
